*avalon-logkit-2.1 (20 Dec 2006)

  20 Dec 2006; Petteri Räty <betelgeuse@gentoo.org>
  +avalon-logkit-2.1.ebuild:
  Version bump. Does not provide jms and javamail use flags any more because
  that option is not available upstream. This ebuild adds support for
  src_test. Fixes bug #158496.

  17 Dec 2006; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  avalon-logkit-2.0-r2.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc wrt bug #157782.

  12 Dec 2006; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org>
  avalon-logkit-2.0-r2.ebuild:
  stable x86, bugs #157782

*avalon-logkit-2.0-r2 (24 Oct 2006)
*avalon-logkit-1.2-r2 (24 Oct 2006)

  24 Oct 2006; Vlastimil Babka <caster@gentoo.org>
  +avalon-logkit-1.2-r2.ebuild, +avalon-logkit-2.0-r2.ebuild:
  Changed jms and javamail dependencies to sun-jms and sun-javamail instead of
  -bin variants (merging changes from migrated-java-experimental-overlay),
  removed openjms and gnu-javamail variants for incompatible package names.
  Fixes bug #152597.

  17 Oct 2006; Joshua Nichols <nichoj@gentoo.org>
  avalon-logkit-1.2-r1.ebuild, avalon-logkit-2.0-r1.ebuild:
  Keyworded ~ia64.

  05 Oct 2006; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org>
  avalon-logkit-1.2.ebuild, avalon-logkit-1.2-r1.ebuild,
  avalon-logkit-2.0.ebuild, avalon-logkit-2.0-r1.ebuild:
  Dropping sparc keywords, see #96229

  22 Jul 2006; Krzysiek Pawlik <nelchael@gentoo.org>
  avalon-logkit-1.2-r1.ebuild, avalon-logkit-2.0-r1.ebuild:
  ant_src_unpack -> src_unpack

